CachedToolbarButtonState

public CachedToolbarButtonState()
Constructor initializes the state of the Delete, Check In, Check Out and Undo Check Out buttons. This is based on the rows in the table provided.

Method Detail

loadState

public boolean loadState(oracle.adf.view.rich.component.UIXTable table,
                         AttachmentsVORowImpl selectedRow)
Based upon the state of the rows in the table provided, determine the state of the Delete, Check In, Check Out and Undo Check Out buttons. This is optimized so that the button state remains un-changed if the document has not changed.

Parameters:
table - data table containing the rows to check.
selectedRow - the single selected row
